You know I can never
promise anything.


993
01:13:15.747 --> 01:13:19.584
But if you want, if you like,
maybe we could see each other again.


994
01:13:20.126 --> 01:13:21.961
It would be okay by me.

995
01:13:22.045 --> 01:13:25.090
It would be more than okay,
it would be... it would be great.


996
01:13:25.173 --> 01:13:27.509
- Alfie, I...
- Yeah?


997
01:13:28.969 --> 01:13:30.262
This is Adam.

998
01:13:34.057 --> 01:13:35.225
Hey, how are you?

999
01:13:36.602 --> 01:13:38.437
- Hey, how you doing, Adam?
- Pretty good.


1000
01:13:38.520 --> 01:13:39.897
