- Yeah.


1001
01:13:46.529 --> 01:13:48.156
It was great running into you.

1002
01:13:50.742 --> 01:13:52.035
You look fantastic.

1003
01:13:52.285 --> 01:13:53.494
Thanks.

1004
01:13:57.332 --> 01:13:59.084
