1018
01:15:39.730 --> 01:15:42.984
- You sure?
- I'm fine. Get out, Alfie.


1019
01:15:43.067 --> 01:15:46.529
I'm sorry. I just... I wanted to see
if I could borrow a car.


1020
01:15:47.530 --> 01:15:48.865
