1021
01:15:49.908 --> 01:15:51.034
Sorry?

1022
01:15:52.160 --> 01:15:55.497
- Blossom leave me.
- Blossom?


1023
01:15:56.998 --> 01:15:58.375
Is that your wife's name, Blossom?

1024
01:15:59.835 --> 01:16:02.880
What I do wrong, Alfie? Love her?

1025
01:16:04.923 --> 01:16:06.258
Hey, look, mate.

1026
01:16:07.092 --> 01:16:09.970
Come on, you can win her back.
Woo her.


1027
01:16:10.054 --> 01:16:13.724
Send flowers and chocolates.
Write a poem.


1028
01:16:14.684 --> 01:16:15.893
