1038
01:17:47.072 --> 01:17:48.240
Hey, Sam.

1039
01:17:48.323 --> 01:17:49.491
Well, that would have been a plan.

1040
01:17:52.035 --> 01:17:53.620
Well, you know, I'm sorry,
it was just...


1041
01:17:55.622 --> 01:17:56.832
It's nice.

1042
01:18:06.384 --> 01:18:08.553
Look, Lonette...

1043
01:18:11.097 --> 01:18:13.725
This is so uncomfortable, I know.

1044
01:18:14.350 --> 01:18:15.685
- Because...
- You don't have to whisper.


1045
01:18:16.102 --> 01:18:17.604
Marlon's not here.

1046
01:18:24.778 --> 01:18:26.279
I really miss you both.

1047
01:18:26.655 --> 01:18:28.573
And I just wondered, maybe...

1048
01:18:30.242 --> 01:18:32.327
Maybe me and you
could put it all behind us


1049
01:18:32.536 --> 01:18:36.457
pretend like it never happened,
and then move forward, you know?


1050
01:18:37.583 --> 01:18:38.709
I just...

1051
01:18:40.461 --> 01:18:42.296
You know, Alfie...

1052
01:18:43.923 --> 01:18:45.925
