1055
01:19:02.317 --> 01:19:04.945
No, you were right the first time.

1056
01:19:33.892 --> 01:19:36.061
<i>Thinking back to that day
at the clinic</i>


1057
01:19:36.144 --> 01:19:39.564
<i>I remember trying to look
in Lon's eyes to see</i>


1058
01:19:39.648 --> 01:19:42.192
<i>if I could even begin to understand
what she was going through</i>


1059
01:19:43.235 --> 01:19:45.737
<i>and how she wouldn't look at me.</i>

1060
01:19:46.780 --> 01:19:47.990
<i>And I think I knew then.</i>

1061
01:19:49.158 --> 01:19:51.118
<i>I just didn't want
to admit it to myself.</i>


1062
01:19:54.163 --> 01:19:55.456
<i>So classically...</i>

1063
01:19:58.793 --> 01:20:00.127
<i>I said nothing.</i>

1064
01:20:01.379 --> 01:20:06.593
I knew there was a good chance
the baby could be Marlon's.


1065
01:20:10.764 --> 01:20:12.015
At least, I hoped.

1066
01:20:14.726 --> 01:20:16.102
This is a lot...

1067
01:20:19.272 --> 01:20:20.607
for me too, Lon.

1068
01:20:50.263 --> 01:20:51.556
Marlon stayed.

1069
01:20:52.724 --> 01:20:53.892
For now.

1070
01:21:03.110 --> 01:21:04.737
Is there anything I can do?

1071
01:21:07.156 --> 01:21:08.908
What are you gonna do, Alfie?

1072
01:21:51.619 --> 01:21:52.662
Hey.

1073
01:21:58.835 --> 01:22:01.379
You know, I never...

1074
01:22:03.214 --> 01:22:05.383
- I never meant...
- You never mean to hurt anybody.


1075
01:22:10.889 --> 01:22:12.140
But you do, Alfie.

1076
01:23:44.487 --> 01:23:46.656
<i>I felt I needed
a friend to talk to.</i>

1077
01:23:47.407 --> 01:23:50.493
<i>Problem was,
they were suddenly in short supply.</i>


1078
01:23:51.160 --> 01:23:53.913
