1080
01:23:56.791 --> 01:23:58.126
And I'm crying.

1081
01:23:58.627 --> 01:24:01.838
- Crying for the little one?
- I don't know exactly.


1082
01:24:04.091 --> 01:24:05.259
Maybe for him.

1083
01:24:07.553 --> 01:24:09.054
Mostly, I think, for me.

1084
01:24:11.807 --> 01:24:13.100
