quite like that before.


1086
01:24:21.192 --> 01:24:24.570
And believe me,
I've had some looks that could kill.


1087
01:24:27.824 --> 01:24:32.328
He stood by Lonette.
I could've never, ever...


1088
01:24:32.787 --> 01:24:35.498
You don't know what you'll do
till you really love someone.


1089
01:24:39.544 --> 01:24:40.754
