1176
01:30:41.464 --> 01:30:42.549
Alfie, please.

1177
01:30:42.632 --> 01:30:44.759
Tell me. Please?

1178
01:30:47.971 --> 01:30:51.016
Really, I would like to know.
What's he got? Tell me.


1179
01:30:52.434 --> 01:30:55.395
I want to know what he's got.
Please tell me.


1180
01:30:56.772 --> 01:30:58.440
Come on...

1181
01:30:59.024 --> 01:31:02.319
Come on, just tell me.
Just tell me, come on.


1182
01:31:04.530 --> 01:31:06.407
