1185
01:31:50.995 --> 01:31:53.456
<i>I've gotta admit,
I didn't see it coming.</i>


1186
01:31:56.084 --> 01:31:57.919
<i>She caught me off-guard, all right.</i>

1187
01:32:00.797 --> 01:32:03.675
