is they have this quiet way


1191
01:32:20.985 --> 01:32:23.070
of sneaking up on you
when you least expect it.


1192
01:32:26.240 --> 01:32:27.492
You know what I mean?

1193
01:32:28.701 --> 01:32:29.786
Yeah.

1194
01:32:31.829 --> 01:32:33.122
Like with Liz.

1195
01:32:34.165 --> 01:32:37.377
Who would've thought,
of all the women I've known...


1196
01:32:40.589 --> 01:32:43.508
the one I let my guard down with
delivers the knockout punch.


1197
01:32:47.304 --> 01:32:48.347
Ironic.

1198
01:32:51.642 --> 01:32:53.060
Calendar word.

1199
01:33:02.195 --> 01:33:03.362
Dorie.

1200
01:33:07.909 --> 01:33:09.619
- Hi.
- Hello, Alfie.


1201
01:33:12.914 --> 01:33:16.418
- I haven't seen you in ages.
- Maybe because you stopped calling.


1202
01:33:17.961 --> 01:33:20.881
I know.
Things were getting a bit too...


1203
01:33:20.964 --> 01:33:23.592
Don't bother explaining.
I'm way past needing excuses.


1204
01:33:23.842 --> 01:33:24.968
All right.

1205
01:33:25.886 --> 01:33:27.930
No, you know what? 
