1207
01:33:30.516 --> 01:33:33.727
Someone cuter came along?
I don't need to hear it, Alfie.


1208
01:33:33.811 --> 01:33:34.895
- Look, Dorie...
- Really.


1209
01:33:34.979 --> 01:33:36.147
Look, Dorie...

